The Followers
by Jean-SÃ©bastien Fauteux

Dependency:
- SFML 2.x (originally built with 2.0 RC)
- Pugixml 1.7

SFML comes as a submodule.
Pugixml comes included in the source code.

First Release: May 2012
Last modification: Mai 15th 2017

Changeset 1.0.3:
-Put SFML as a Submodule
-Removed useless Pugixml lib
-Updated Copyrights and license

Changeset 1.0.2:
-Convert to CMake
-Removed useless boost dependancy
-Removed code specific to Windows.


